title: Aura Icon Pack v2.7.1 APK (Android)
description:
Aura icon pack features a gorgeous color palette consisting of 6 colors. You'll notice shapes and specific elements have a raised shadow, similar to my Elementary icon pack. These help the companion colors really pop. Each icon is made from scratch as vectors on a 512px canvas, and sized down to 192px to ensure no quality loss.

Extras included in the dashboard app:
Material inspired dashboard
Many alternative icons labeled alphabetically
Tap on any icon to get the app name
Smart icon request
Dynamic Calendar icon support
30+ original wallpapers
Now featuring 1300 icons and daily updates, leading into weekly updates

Launchers Supported:
Action Launcher Pro
Action Launcher 3
ADW
ADW EX
Apex
Atom
Aviate
CM Theme Engine
Go(switch off "icon mask" in Preferences) 
Holo
Inspire
KitKat
TSF
Unicon and Beautiful Icon Styler apps should work with stock launchers, as well as CM theme engine with this app**

What's in this version : (Updated : 8 April 2016)

Aura v2.7.1 fixes the icon request system. If you sent it within the last 24 hours, please try 1 more time
Aura now contains over 2,350 icons :-)
Aura Zooper is available on Google Play for free with over 70 matching zooper widgets to compliment Aura's color palette.
Please rate/review if you haven't already, and thanks so very much for your amazing support. I have a new project releasing on 4/20 so please lookout for it :-)
Required Android O/S : 4.0+
